00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:34,310
You're taking me for granted
on our first day together, huh?

324
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:37,930
I'll pull out all your flowers.

325
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:43,690
Go ahead. You're experienced. You've done it once.

326
00:27:43,690 --> 00:27:45,290
