397
00:33:16,690 --> 00:33:20,830
Amusement park again? I'm way too old for this.

398
00:33:21,690 --> 00:33:24,370
- How old are you? 
 - I'm eight years old.

399
00:33:24,370 --> 00:33:28,110
Eight-year-olds love amusement parks. Let's go.

400
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:30,410
No way. I'm not going.

401
00:33:30,410 --> 00:33:32,210
Come on.

402
00:33:32,870 --> 00:33:34,570
So cute.

403
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:52,030
- Come. 
 - I'm not going. It's scary.

404
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:56,630
