479
00:39:08,210 --> 00:39:11,950
- Where is Wang Si Si? 
 - She left. Her mom picked her up.

480
00:39:11,950 --> 00:39:13,870
Here.

481
00:39:13,870 --> 00:39:15,430
Want to head back first?

482
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:17,730
I'll take Jia Yu to a bubble tea shop

483
00:39:17,730 --> 00:39:19,930
to do homework, and walk him home.

484
00:39:19,930 --> 00:39:23,710
No, since we came together,
we should leave together.

485
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:26,830
Someone's picking him up.

486
00:39:26,830 --> 00:39:28,630
Who?

487
00:39:30,530 --> 00:39:32,670
What's the emergency?

488
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:34,790
Pick him up.

489
00:39:34,790 --> 00:39:36,730
Him?

490
00:39:36,730 --> 00:39:37,990
Let's go.

491
00:39:37,990 --> 00:39:39,870
That tutoring will come in handy.

492
00:39:39,870 --> 00:39:41,750
You studied?

493
00:39:41,750 --> 00:39:43,930
No, don't listen to him.

494
00:39:43,930 --> 00:39:45,850
- Why did you get tutoring?
- It's my hobby.

495
00:39:45,850 --> 00:39:47,030
Let's go, too.

496
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:50,100
I like the Olympiad. Let me teach you.

497
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:52,177
I've finished all those exercises already.

498
00:40:05,090 --> 00:40:06,350
Why'd you come up?

499
00:40:06,350 --> 00:40:09,050
To keep you company. It's chilly.

500
00:40:09,050 --> 00:40:10,650
Come on.

501
00:40:25,830 --> 00:40:27,630
