502
00:40:28,830 --> 00:40:30,930
Can I ask you something?

503
00:40:31,870 --> 00:40:33,470
Go ahead.

504
00:40:34,350 --> 00:40:41,090
I wasn't your boyfriend, but now I am.
So, I'm entitled to ask you this.

505
00:40:41,090 --> 00:40:42,570
