537
00:42:30,890 --> 00:42:37,450
Explain your relationship with Jiang Lu Zhi.

538
00:42:37,450 --> 00:42:40,350
Jiang Lu Zhi wasn't my girlfriend.

539
00:42:40,350 --> 00:42:42,270
