- And you were mean.

545
00:42:57,350 --> 00:42:58,830
It's totally different.

546
00:42:58,830 --> 00:43:01,270
How? Explain now.

547
00:43:01,270 --> 00:43:02,970
Different how? Tell me.

548
00:43:02,970 --> 00:43:05,350
I couldn't fake it with you
to lie to Grandma, right?

549
00:43:05,350 --> 00:43:07,010
Why not?

550
00:43:07,010 --> 00:43:10,570
Because I like you.

551
00:43:10,570 --> 00:43:15,430
Say it to the sun.

552
